{"sn5.7:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 5.7 ","sn5.7:0.2":"1. Bhikkhunivagga ","sn5.7:0.3":"Upacalasutta ","sn5.7:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn5.7:1.2":"Atha kho upacala bhikkhuni pubbanhasamayam nivasetva …pe… ","sn5.7:1.3":"annatarasmim rukkhamule divaviharam nisidi. ","sn5.7:1.4":"Atha kho maro papima yena upacala bhikkhuni tenupasankami; upasankamitva upacalam bhikkhunim etadavoca: ","sn5.7:1.5":"“kattha nu tvam, bhikkhuni, uppajjitukama”ti? ","sn5.7:1.6":"“Na khvaham, avuso, katthaci uppajjitukama”ti. ","sn5.7:2.1":"“Tavatimsa ca yama ca, ","sn5.7:2.2":"tusita capi devata; ","sn5.7:2.3":"Nimmanaratino deva, ","sn5.7:2.4":"ye deva vasavattino; ","sn5.7:2.5":"Tattha cittam panidhehi, ","sn5.7:2.6":"ratim paccanubhossasi”ti. ","sn5.7:3.1":"“Tavatimsa ca yama ca, ","sn5.7:3.2":"tusita capi devata; ","sn5.7:3.3":"Nimmanaratino deva, ","sn5.7:3.4":"ye deva vasavattino; ","sn5.7:3.5":"Kamabandhanabaddha te, ","sn5.7:3.6":"enti maravasam puna. ","sn5.7:4.1":"Sabbo adipito loko, ","sn5.7:4.2":"sabbo loko padhupito; ","sn5.7:4.3":"Sabbo pajjalito loko, ","sn5.7:4.4":"sabbo loko pakampito. ","sn5.7:5.1":"Akampitam apajjalitam, ","sn5.7:5.2":"aputhujjanasevitam; ","sn5.7:5.3":"Agati yattha marassa, ","sn5.7:5.4":"tattha me nirato mano”ti. ","sn5.7:6.1":"Atha kho maro papima “janati mam upacala bhikkhuni”ti dukkhi dummano tatthevantaradhayiti. "}